{"tid":1821232,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"國際線要十卜，今次終於黎到北歐!!!!!!","createTime":"2020-01-12T06:06:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-18T13:52:20.000Z","uid":38864,"like":136,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":72,"replies":[{"pid":"63d4c9b16bcda788f3adac0bdfb7c63e20e58e48","tid":1821232,"uid":38864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T06:06:36.000Z","msg":"借朋友 account post:<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">挪威嘅手足會响2月邀請一班香港手足去首都Oslo。為左好好運用時間同資源，佢地今次仲夾埋丹麥同瑞典嘅手足搞個北歐巡遊訪問</span></span><br />\n<br />\n係呀，提名香港人拎2020年諾貝爾和平獎嘅執政黨國會議員 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Guri Melby</span></span> 會同呢班香港手足見面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔止，挪威响兩個最大城市(首都Oslo同Bergen) 籌備緊反送中運動新聞攝影展<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">佢地啱啱推出左個眾籌計劃：<br />\n<a href=\"https://goget.fund/2FIgrwh\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoget.fund%2F2FIgrwh&d=uClJ75VMDgyJ2T8QnpTVXYuQyocENDzUuJTHoiHzCac%3D&h=8050b607\" target=\"_blank\">https://goget.fund/2FIgrwh</a><br />\n大家支持一下! </span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n光時<br />\n復代<br />\n香革<br />\n港命"},{"pid":"f41885fe260e3da0a206f7c253f89437d140d238","tid":1821232,"uid":314380,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T07:13:16.000Z","msg":"Push !!!"},{"pid":"24ab5c1833b17dfca63f7742bae232a926a93078","tid":1821232,"uid":314380,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T07:14:39.000Z","msg":"Norway 手足好勁！"},{"pid":"7717bd925e14bfddea715d721cefb075cc90a2f1","tid":1821232,"uid":38864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T11:04:50.000Z","msg":"Push!!!!"},{"pid":"7f77206709a10e1092ffd3696fd4d5389ba72e82","tid":1821232,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T11:05:17.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f84f8ab767ef4ceeb0c86e13c782de9aa3049abf","tid":1821232,"uid":61287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T11:06:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a5a349728df95422bbfb5386fd07149c8d1c06fa","tid":1821232,"uid":158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T11:14:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"332d5889dd1c7301a4edcdc882189675302037c7","tid":1821232,"uid":54564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T11:22:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68855c183110d62d6838b4ed8cacb08a4ad725b8","tid":1821232,"uid":5298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T12:07:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a02cceae89f74545c5c264729c048be58609fccc","tid":1821232,"uid":83557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T12:26:55.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"3a6b88b374eeed399a4e5aec76c220d61c4b513d","tid":1821232,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T12:56:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"650bc8d5aae4e4573ec82babd01efb39248d57af","tid":1821232,"uid":301663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T22:07:42.000Z","msg":"推!!!!!<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af5d96b816a57627f41b11bdb83d11f7b7de40b2","tid":1821232,"uid":240204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T23:21:34.000Z","msg":"推推推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06347eadb0d4ea377815f986fdc49833afa9428c","tid":1821232,"uid":207614,"lik